# The send_emails functionality of utils.py depends on a
# ~/.msmtprc (configuration) file with the following content.
# (...but without the password being redacted.)
# see:
# https://websistent.com/how-to-use-msmtp-with-gmail-yahoo-and-php-mail/
# Also: ~/.msmtp.log
#
account gmail
tls on
auth on
host smtp.gmail.com
port 587
# the club's gmail account:
user rodandboatclub
from rodandboatclub@gmail.com
password **redacted**

